    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\udc4b Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014it basically still has that 'new car' smell. I've taken such good care of it, you won't find a single blemish. It drives like a total dream! If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one. Come take a look, you're going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
