    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S RX-7 is a peerless example of rotary engineering, featuring the original 13B-REW power plant with its sophisticated sequential twin-turbocharger setup intact. The chassis remains factory-spec, preserving the surgical precision of its four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and near-perfect 50:50 weight distribution. Every mechanical component\u2014from the Torsen limited-slip differential to the crisp five-speed manual gearbox\u2014operates with showroom-level tactile feedback. The vacuum lines have been meticulously maintained to ensure seamless boost transition, and the apex seals show optimal compression across all faces. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the purist who demands mechanical integrity and unadulterated performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2021 model. Mint condition. Single owner. No accidents. Garage kept. Clean title. Full service history included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
