      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved by a single enthusiast owner. This car is in pristine condition, having spent its life in a climate-controlled garage under a soft cover. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster, enhanced by a professional ceramic coating, and shows absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state; the premium leather seats are firm with zero bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule example for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection. Included are all original manuals, two master keys, and the original window sticker.",
